  Keywords: War, Game, Korea, Map, Mouse, 2 Player

  Short description: A 2 player War game played on a map of the Korean
  peninsula.

  Description: A board type, war-game for 2 players played on a map of
	       The Korean peninsula. Map has 2,4,8, & 12 X zoom capabilities.
	       Each player has 80 combat units including: Infantry, Armor,
	       Air Calvary, & Marines. The map has roads, rivers, mountains
	       & cities and was drawn to accurately simulate the terrain of
	       Korea. There is no time limit on the game, the players
	       move their units and attack each other using the mouse
	       for all movement. Mouse activated "buttons" and windows
	       on the display make the game easy to learn & use.
	       Players have the option of saving games in a file.


